Bedrock evaluation job.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ModelIdentifier => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the evaluator model for custom
metrics. For a list of supported evaluator models, see Evaluate model
performance using another LLM as a judge
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/bedrock/latest/userguide/evaluation-judge.html)
